==Unlocking blue==
===Read-tag===
* {{tbox|I sell tools that chop. Near where adventurers begin. Come visit my shop.}}
* {{tact|end}}

===Talking to Bob===
* {{topt|I have a present for you!}}
** '''Player:''' I have a present for you!
** '''Bob:''' Lovely! I've been waiting for you to turn up!
** '''Player:''' You've been waiting for me?
** '''Bob:''' Yes! Didn't anybody tell you? This present is actually for you!
** '''Player:''' For me?
** '''Bob:''' All for you. Every time you deliver it, you'll unlock a new colour of wrapping paper for it.
** '''Bob:''' It's a pretty magical present!
** '''Player:''' That sounds pretty cool! So I can change its colour?
** '''Bob:''' Yep. Look, you can change its wrapping paper to blue now.
** {{tact|Bob performs an enchant animation and unlocks the new colour.}}
** {{tbox|pic=Secret santa present (blue) detail.png|You've unlocked blue wrapping paper for your present.}}
** '''Player:''' That's so cool! Who do I deliver it to next?
** '''Bob:''' You'll have to figure that out for yourself, that's the fun. Check the name tag!
** '''Bob:''' I'm going to get back to work, good luck.
** {{tact|end}}
* {{topt|event=No|Talk about other things.}}

