===Talking to Malignius Mortifer===
* {{topt|I have a present for you!}}
** '''Player:''' I have a present for you!
** '''Malignius Mortifer:''' I see. Let's do this quickly, I am quite busy.
** {{tact|Malignius Mortifer performs an enchant animation and unlocks the new colour.}}
** {{tbox|pic=Secret santa present (gold) detail.png|You've unlocked gold wrapping paper for your present.}}
** '''Player:''' Thank you!
** '''Malignius Mortifer:''' You've completed your tasks, well done.
** '''Player:''' You were the last one?
** '''Malignius Mortifer:''' Yes. Always save the best until last.
** '''Player:''' You're the best?
** '''Malignius Mortifer:''' Obviously, I am Malignius Mortifer.
** '''Player:''' Ah yes, the great Malignius Mortifer...
** '''Malignius Mortifer:''' You don't think I'm great?
** '''Malignius Mortifer:''' How about if I turn you into a mushroom. What will you think then, [player name]?
** {{tact|Malignius Mortifer turns the player into a mushroom.}}
** '''Player:''' MMMmmph!
** {{tact|end}}
* {{topt|event=No|Talk about other things.}}

